Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fetal dismemberment surgery.\N- Cutting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutting the foal inside the mother horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's at least save the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don’t cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- It’s crying "Stop!"\N- What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop! Let go!\N- Calm down, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don’t do that!\N- It’s to save Fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Snow Pearl?\NWe named it Snow Pearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised! We promised\Nto watch its growth forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can’t do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just… something like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If that’s how you feel, then quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s better to stop aiming\Nto be a veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ENGLISH SUBTITLE BY CHRIZ KAYRIKO\NVisit chrizkayriko.github.io
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, if you’d like, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, did you start working?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… but is it really\Nokay to take this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s fine, it’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Our kids have long since left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just the two of us,\Nwe can’t eat this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Isn’t that Satori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for suddenly coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s okay, come home whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasted money on a plane ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m happy to see your face, Satori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you start working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In work, an old hairdresser\Nfriend reached out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so I decided to help with kimono dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have work tomorrow too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A customer is coming in for a pre-shoot\Nfor their coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko’s {\i1}furisode{\i0} from her\Ncoming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:21.11,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(TN: Furisode is a type of\Ntraditional Japanese kimono.)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mother’s?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- You’ve seen it in photos, right?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother was grinning\Nfrom ear to ear in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it would be\Ndifficult to live until twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve heard she had a\Ncongenital heart condition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But mother passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At 36.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it scary… giving birth to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Because childbirth can\Nbring unexpected things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we eat something delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sukiyaki{\i0}? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.86,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(TN: Sukiyaki is a Japanese hot pot dish.)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sushi{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:55.97,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(TN: Sushi is a traditional Japanese dish that consists\Nof vinegared rice combined with various ingredients.)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Premium {\i1}unagi{\i0}! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:59.38,Notes,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(TN: Unagi is the Japanese\Nword for freshwater eel.)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was just an omelet really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I wanted to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,About earlier… childbirth…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When that child got married and said,\N"I want to have a baby," I was against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really something\NI should tell you, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pregnancy itself puts\Nstrain on her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and risking one's body just to give\Nbirth. I thought it would be better not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:06:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa and everyone else around\Nwere worried and tried to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But that child wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Said, "I've had to hold back on so\Nmany things because of my illness."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That child, who rarely ever\Ncries, let the tears flow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She said all the patience until now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,was time spent becoming stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So… it's okay, it's not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're scared, you can't\Nmake dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave birth to you, risking life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grandma’s omelet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tasted like Mom’s cooking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,LILAC NO HANASAKU KEMONOMICHI\N(THE PATH WHERE LILACS BLOOM)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 2/3: THE MEANING OF BEING BORN\NSatori! This is bad! Wake up, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Watermelon delivery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ehh?! Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why are you running?\N- Hey! Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, coming all the way from\NHokkaido, that’s so kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take your time and relax, okay?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori, grandma has work, kimono dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- I didn't come here just for this.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be passing by.\NStopping by on the way home to Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry for worrying you.\N- I'm not worried at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- I did, though. But I didn’t!\N- Satori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Another friend is here. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I chased after migrating birds and\Nbefore realizing it, I ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I caused everyone to\Nworry. I'm really pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kubo-kun, Ayaka…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kubo-kun," huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m just "Ayaka," but\Nit’s "Kubo-kun," huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… Showing off, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, could it be his\Nname isn’t remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s fine, fine, fine.\NNo, um, it's not that…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kubo-kun, huh. His\Nname is Kubo Toritaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why say such a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and eat\Nthe watermelon, Toritaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna eat it without being told.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it, it's Zansetsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Zan" as in unfortunate,\N"setsu" as in falling snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The name comes from a bird. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In the story "Old Daizo and a wild goose,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,there’s a goose named Zansetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father named it,\Nright? The ornithologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is an ornithologist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He studies bird ecology and the\Nconservation of endemic species
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and did ecological surveys\Ntogether since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up naturally feeling close to birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Try reading "Old Daizo and a wild goose" sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:11:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it? Maybe animals\Nare far more dignified than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even someone like me, who isn’t an\Nanimal lover, ended up feeling that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not an animal lover?\NHuh? That’s unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm just not super passionate about them.\N- Then why veterinary medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you eat watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At home, my mother carefully removed the\Nseeds and cut it into bite-sized pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to just bite into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, on the other hand, made my two\Nolder brothers take medical school exams
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but for me, he said,\N"Since you're a girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,just go to the affiliated\Nwomen's university."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to rebel against such parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And as expected, I totally shocked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said, "I'm going to be a\Nveterinarian" they were speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want became\Na vet to shock your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it was shallow. Now, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Satori, who truly loves\Nanimals and wants to help them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't aim to be a vet with such feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so maybe it doesn’t suit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too… After all this,\Nmaybe I can't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to give up on\Nbecoming a vet. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If Satori thinks it's impossible, then for\Nme, it’s a hundred times more impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I also…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,…would like to confess something here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- but nothing.\N- Nothing? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about studying veterinary\Nmedicine, any confusion or anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- None.\N- Aren’t the practicals tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.\N- Doubts or worries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- None.\N- Nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,None. Really, nothing at all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bird-boy, who has not a single\Ncloud of doubt, is dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there’s not much to say, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just be quiet already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, why not take\Na bite of the watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat it however you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat watermelon and\Nlive life the way you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eating watermelon and laughing together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking about it,\Nsomething as simple as that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it was like a miracle for someone like\Nme, who had stopped going to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not so easy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Write down the recipe after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll have it ready for the\Nnext time you come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it’s made\Naccording to the recipe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,there’s no guarantee it will be\Nclose to your Mom’s taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t come back. I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I come back,\NI’ll bring souvenirs too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll properly return\Nhome. Not just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for souvenirs. I’ve\Nalready received enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that such wonderful\Nfriends were made over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the best souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It’s not like the anxiety\Nis completely gone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I keep running away\Nlike this, I’ll regret it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I’ll end up spending my\Nwhole life unable to do anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A life of only running\Naway is not what I want.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you for your hard work.\N- Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oimo-chan was such a good girl today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- If anything comes up again.\N- Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A phone call would’ve sufficed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought it’d be better\Nto talk in person after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the one Kishimoto-san rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?\NIs everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is there a problem?\N- No, all fine now. It's doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not being able to find an owner\Nto take in the dog was a big issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, Dr. Hisatsune\Nhas decided to take it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get your consent for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If Dr. Hisatsune is going to\Ntake care of it, that’s a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.16,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to take it\Nin as a blood donor dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood donor dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog that donates blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Blood donation…\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when dogs\Nneed blood transfusions too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,in Japan right now, there is\Nno blood bank for animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so there need to be dogs that can share\Ntheir blood for sick or injured dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it cruel to take blood\Nfrom a dog to save another?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s true that there is pain when a\Nneedle is inserted. There may also be fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be changes in physical\Ncondition due to blood being drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But by becoming a blood donor dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog that was abandoned by its owner can\Nfind a new role and live in a new place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you consider it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Some dogs are treasured for\Nlife without needing to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,while others are thrown away like\Ngarbage when they are no longer wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there are those\Nthat become blood donor dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and work to save the lives of other dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you meet Shizuhara?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet once and have a proper talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Veterinarians treat animal\Nillnesses and save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I only imagined that convenient,\Nidealized version of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Having an ideal image of\Nany job is important, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not really an ideal… My\Nthinking was just too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s true that being a veterinarian is\Nnot only about saving animals’ lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, it also involves making\Nthe difficult decision to end a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But those decisions vary\Nfrom person to person,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and they change with time and culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, wouldn’t it be fine for you\Nto approach it in your own way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- My own way?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You heal animals’ illnesses and save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, “I will only do this,”\Nand only do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing in this world\Nthat absolutely must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pronger, you’re in a great mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The cafeteria menu is going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the hamburger steak set meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone’s favorite hamburger\Nsteak set meal isn’t changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They use a mix of beef and\Npork, right? That’s okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't the cows and pigs\Nmade into hamburgers pitiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's contradictory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I like hamburgers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, for the rest\Nof my life, hamburgers…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding, I will eat them.\NBecause they’re delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.82,0:23:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will eat them with\Na feeling of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm full of contradictions. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to help a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please brush Pronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My late father was also a veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.32,0:23:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- From Kase-kun?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a clinical\Nveterinarian for racehorses,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he handles treatment\Nfor illnesses and injuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.41,0:23:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,vaccinations, and\Ndisease prevention work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.16,0:23:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,On race days, he examined\Nthe horses that were going to run,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.82,0:24:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and in case of an injury or accident,\Nhe carried out rescue operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.99,0:24:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he was quite skilled\Nand an excellent veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.99,0:24:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, he quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.16,0:24:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, do you know what\Nhappens to a horse that can no longer run
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.93,0:24:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,or suffers a fatal injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Some get taken in by riding clubs or\Nretirement farms and can live in a new place
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.03,0:24:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but some are euthanized.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.82,0:24:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, as a veterinarian,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.16,0:24:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,he was in a position where\Nhe had to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.66,0:24:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Dr. Nomi made the\Ndecision during Fairy’s birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.49,0:25:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.98,0:25:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and my father always\Nenthusiastically told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.70,0:25:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"I became a veterinarian\Nto save animals."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.82,0:25:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked about it with so much joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.82,0:25:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For my father, being forced to\Nmake life-and-death decisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.82,0:25:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it must have been extremely painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.16,0:25:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a toll on his mental health,\Nand after resigning, he passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.49,0:25:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He took his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.66,0:25:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just loving animals isn’t always\Nenough to overcome things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.49,0:25:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be more\Nlives that cannot be saved
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.41,0:25:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,than those that can be\Nsaved as a veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.32,0:26:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of animals we humans\Ncan save might be very limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.82,0:26:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I will become a veterinarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.32,0:26:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become a veterinarian
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.95,0:26:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and embrace both the hopes\Nand despair that my father saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.82,0:26:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,For my father’s sake as\Nwell… I will cherish every life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.66,0:26:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.32,0:26:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking about life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.66,0:26:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whether it’s animals or humans…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking about the preciousness\Nof life born into this world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.56,0:27:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking about its fleeting nature...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.82,0:27:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thinking about human selfishness,\Ncontradictions, convenience, and limitations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.49,0:27:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each time, resolving to\Nmove forward, yet wavering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.89,0:27:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes, wanting to run away again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.59,0:27:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being supported by those\Naround, and recovering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.82,0:27:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuu, come! Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.05,0:28:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes gaining\Nconfidence, sometimes losing it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.66,0:28:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.07,0:28:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through repeating such things,\Ndays pass in the blink of an eye.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.66,0:29:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayaka, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.66,0:29:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break over\Nthere. Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.98,0:29:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.16,0:29:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.49,0:29:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To honor precious lives,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.32,0:29:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with a sincere resolve\Nthat surpasses mere pity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.16,0:29:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we dedicate ourselves to\Nlearning with all our hearts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.32,0:29:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a whooper swan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.49,0:29:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The shape of the black markings\Non the beak is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.49,0:29:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When they become adults,\Neach one has a unique marking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.32,0:29:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s how they can be\Nindividually identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.82,0:30:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which one?\N- That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.66,0:30:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.99,0:30:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori and Zansetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.49,0:30:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You guys get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.49,0:30:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.66,0:30:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not just date already?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.99,0:30:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t really get what “dating” means.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.49,0:30:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How is “being close friends”\Ndifferent from “dating”?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.82,0:30:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.99,0:30:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, the difference from a friend is\Nwhether there's romantic feelings involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.82,0:30:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you like friends too,\Nso you become close, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.49,0:30:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel nervous when you’re with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.66,0:30:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, want to see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.66,0:30:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A long-tailed tit I photographed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.16,0:30:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Flying in the winter sky\Nwhile snow was falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.99,0:31:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t feel nervous when\Nyou’re with a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.66,0:31:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Long-tailed tits have insulating\Nfeathers, so they’re resistant to the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.16,0:31:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, see this? It’s all fluffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.16,0:31:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to talk more, to know\Nmore, never wanting to be apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.49,0:31:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to always\Nbe by this person’s side.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.49,0:31:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in winter, they can\Nsurvive by sucking on tree sap.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.49,0:31:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Something feels really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.32,0:31:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.16,0:31:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to give this\Nperson’s side to anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.16,0:31:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Zansetsu-senpai. Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.16,0:31:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go ahead.\N- Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.16,0:31:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.49,0:31:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, about the upcoming test, there's\Nsomething I don’t understand…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.16,0:31:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad! No romantic feelings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.66,0:32:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's comfortable being together,\Neasy, and he gives a sense of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.66,0:32:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Love for animals and\Nromantic love are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.32,0:32:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.32,0:32:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.49,0:32:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something important to\Ntalk about with Kishimoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.99,0:32:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh? With me?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.99,0:32:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grandma,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.16,0:32:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the first time, I went to a café\Nwith an adult man, just the two of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.16,0:32:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.49,0:32:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The most popular item in\Nthe café is called crème brûlée.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.16,0:32:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The top part is burnt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.32,0:33:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto-san does\Nthat kind of thing too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.87,0:33:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't say it was to send to grandma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.16,0:33:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.16,0:33:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.82,0:33:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With graduation approaching,\Nthings are going to get busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.99,0:33:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The national exam\Nis also coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.16,0:33:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there won’t be much time to\Ngo to Nanakamado Animal Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.66,0:33:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why, would you like\Nto work there in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.66,0:33:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... At Nanakamado Animal Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.82,0:33:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there will be\Na part-time wage,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.82,0:33:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and actually, Dr. Hisatsune\Nhas already given permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.99,0:33:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I don’t think I’m\Ncapable of working yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.16,0:33:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- I think I’d just be a burden.\N- No need to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.82,0:34:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first started working at that\Nhospital, I was still in my second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.16,0:34:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hisatsune isn’t expecting\Nimmediate results from you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.49,0:34:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a desire of her to\Nteach you knowledge and skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.99,0:34:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, just think of it as\Nan opportunity to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.82,0:34:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- I volunteer!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.82,0:34:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah... she’s also from Hokuno University.\N- I enrolled this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.32,0:34:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Kase-san through\Nanimal rescue volunteering.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.99,0:34:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a first-year, isn’t working\Nat an animal hospital still too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.66,0:34:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said to work while learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.99,0:34:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what I said just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.32,0:34:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If it’s for Kase-san, I’ll quit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.32,0:34:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.32,0:34:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh? It’s not about good or bad...\N- Then I’ll...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.82,0:34:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll do it!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.32,0:34:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If I’m okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.99,0:35:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Then, I will accept the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.66,0:35:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.16,0:35:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.49,0:35:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, one more time.\NWhat did Kase-san say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.82,0:35:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm so glad."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.16,0:35:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.99,0:35:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm so glad... I’ve always..."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.66,0:35:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve always thought\NKishimoto-san was the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.43,0:35:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Nanakamado. At\NNanakamado Animal Hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.49,0:35:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,taking over Kase's position and\Nworking there, it's best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.32,0:35:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that,\Nbut your face is smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.96,0:35:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.99,0:35:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grinning.\N- Not grinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.00,0:35:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For that reason... I’ve\Ndecided to start a part-time job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.66,0:35:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.66,0:35:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you're getting used\Nto it, I will drop by too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.99,0:35:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without overdoing it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.32,0:36:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of course, studies come first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.82,0:36:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.82,0:36:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When the part-time job savings add up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.16,0:36:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will invite grandma to Hokkaido.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.49,0:36:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come visit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.82,0:36:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's eat crème brûlée together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.32,0:36:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chidori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.66,0:36:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you shouldn't be awake.\NYou should be sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.66,0:36:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.49,0:36:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is this okay?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.99,0:36:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Should I make rice porridge?\N- It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.32,0:36:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fine, right?\NShould you call Satori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.99,0:36:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only saying "it's fine," geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.92,0:36:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,ORAL MEDICINE
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.43,0:36:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.99,0:36:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know Yamame and Sakuramasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.82,0:36:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fish?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.49,0:37:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly the same species\Nof the salmon family.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.99,0:37:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they grow up, they are\Ncalled Yamame and Sakuramasu
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.66,0:37:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- with different names.\N- Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.49,0:37:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's whether they grew up\Nin the river or in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.66,0:37:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That difference changes their name?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.16,0:37:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Then, why do they grow up\Nin different places, river and sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.49,0:37:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That is because of the strength of the\Nindividual fish during the fry stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.16,0:37:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, fry that are\Nbig and strong as individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.99,0:37:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,can get food where they were\Nborn, so they stay in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.99,0:37:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, fry\Nthat are small and weak
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.66,0:37:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,descend the river searching\Nfor food and head to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.66,0:37:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea has an abundance of\Nfood incomparable to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.49,0:37:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the fry that manage\Nto survive in the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.82,0:37:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,can grow much bigger than\Nthose that stayed in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.49,0:37:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamame that grew in the river\Nat most reach around 30 cm,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.99,0:38:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,while Sakuramasu that grew\Nin the sea can reach 50 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.32,0:38:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A complete reversal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.49,0:38:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a complete reversal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.16,0:38:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if small and weak…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.16,0:38:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there are hardships\Nand one runs away,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.66,0:38:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with time, change is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.16,0:38:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have suffered are stronger than\Nthose who could do everything from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.99,0:38:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.82,0:38:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you're with friends,\Nyou don't feel nervous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.66,0:39:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.49,0:39:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten late. Let's\Ngo straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.82,0:39:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to talk more,\Nlearn more, you don't want to be apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.16,0:39:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be\Nnext to this person forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.28,0:39:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to let anyone be next to this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.73,0:39:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.55,0:39:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… the seatbelt…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.49,0:39:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.32,0:39:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.82,0:39:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.82,0:40:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Sapporo. A friend\Nfrom high school is visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.82,0:40:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be introduced to someone\Nspecial. Someone nice for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.16,0:40:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- I hope there's someone who suits Mako.\N- I'm getting excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.16,0:40:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Mr. Kishimoto going?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.32,0:40:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, this kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.66,0:40:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You should make up your mind already.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.99,0:40:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, how much longer\Nare you going to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.16,0:40:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ehh?\N- "Ehh? What are you talking about?"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.49,0:40:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb, it's Kase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.77,0:40:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kase-san... You can do\Nit, do it! Confess already!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.54,0:40:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Christmas is for this! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.17,0:40:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck. Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.64,0:40:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.23,0:40:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm off.\N- Take care. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.87,0:40:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take care.\N- Seems fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.49,0:40:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Zansetsu-kun? What\Nare you doing for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.16,0:40:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuhara-san, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.72,0:40:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always busy with exam studies.\NMaybe I'll just relax this Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.66,0:41:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.10,0:41:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto-san, can\Nyou pass me that red one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.32,0:41:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.17,0:41:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.99,0:41:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised to go to\NFurano to eat soup curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.32,0:41:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.82,0:41:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- So this is what you're doing.\N- Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.82,0:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto-san, are you\Ngoing too? He's treating us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.99,0:41:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.99,0:41:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishimoto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.16,0:41:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, at Nanakamado, have\Nyou gotten used to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.82,0:41:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. Thanks to\NDr. Hisatsune, I’m managing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.82,0:42:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a privately owned animal hospital, so\Na lot of different pet owners come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.99,0:42:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Soup curry.\N- I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.82,0:42:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really that hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.32,0:42:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one who\Nsaid you wanted to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.99,0:42:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about Christmas?\N- I am just going to relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.99,0:42:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, "relaxing" means...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.32,0:42:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drive to Furano.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.82,0:42:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if you don’t want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.99,0:42:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, it’s just that I'm in\Nthe mood for soup curry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.16,0:42:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.66,0:43:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah... sorry.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.99,0:43:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... Zansetsu-kun's?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.32,0:43:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... I chose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.66,0:43:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.32,0:43:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it’s a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.78,0:43:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.66,0:43:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.16,0:43:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How do birds find their partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.90,0:43:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With their feathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.99,0:43:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Feathers?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.66,0:43:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The patterns on birds’\Nfeathers have meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.32,0:43:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and they help identify if\Nthey're the same species.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.66,0:44:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,While flying, they instinctively look for\Npatterns on feathers that are the same as theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.82,0:44:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They search instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.16,0:44:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. From there, they find\Na partner and become a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.49,0:44:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, not just a pair, but it\Nalso helps them form a flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.66,0:44:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there's also\N"calling" to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.82,0:44:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.32,0:44:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What about humans? I wonder\Nif humans are the same as birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.16,0:44:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they choose someone who suits them?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.81,0:44:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.99,0:44:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In romance, you might fall for\Nsomeone completely opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.49,0:44:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you're going to be together for life,\Nsomeone with the same values works better.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.82,0:44:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s more likely to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.49,0:44:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? You talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.99,0:44:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Really?\N- Ah, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.73,0:45:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.12,0:45:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.82,0:45:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not have much advice, but
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.66,0:45:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should express your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.82,0:45:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.96,0:45:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to\Nregret not saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.82,0:45:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.16,0:45:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I really talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.49,0:45:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.82,0:45:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.16,0:45:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But before I could express\Nmy feelings, I got rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.99,0:45:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn’t express them,\Nso you weren’t rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.66,0:45:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From how it looks, Kase-san\Nand Shizuhara-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.49,0:45:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They might just be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.99,0:46:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a good relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.99,0:46:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re close too, but\Nwe’re just friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.82,0:46:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.82,0:46:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.32,0:46:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.82,0:46:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.32,0:46:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I want feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.75,0:46:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,HOKUNO UNIVERSITY\NAKEBONO DORMITORY
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.82,0:47:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As expected, I couldn’t\Ntell my grandmother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.82,0:47:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn’t even get to confess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.34,0:47:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,MERRY CHRISTMAS
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.30,0:47:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fact that I ended up heartbroken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.88,0:47:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Merry christmas," I\Njust typed that and sent it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.25,0:48:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't notice that it hadn't\Nbeen read until the next morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.32,0:48:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,UNKNOWN NUMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.99,0:48:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.82,0:48:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.88,0:48:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the first time\Nhearing it in a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.32,0:48:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was my father's voice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.32,0:48:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.10,0:48:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.82,0:48:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who have lived\Nbelieving in animals more than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.99,0:48:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as you live, you live together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.82,0:48:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as there's the will,\Nyou can start over in any life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.49,0:48:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to witness the\Npassing of the baton of life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.23,0:48:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,UPON CONSULTING WITH EXPERTS,\NNO ANIMALS WERE HARMED WHILE FILIMING.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.96,0:49:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,ENGLISH SUBTITLES BY CHRIZ KAYRIKO\NVisit chrizkayriko.github.io
